# Installation steps to setup SASS

1. Installed nvm (Node Version Manager) by running:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Restarted the terminal.

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16

4. Verified node version with:
   node -v

5. Installed SASS globally with:
   npm install -g sass@3.7.4

6. Verified SASS installation:
   sass --version
